<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="prove-v">prove <strong><em>v</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /pruːv/    美 /pruːv/  </p>
<p>(proved, proved / proven)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>证明；证实：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Riis believed that poverty caused crime, and he used photos to help him <strong>prove his point</strong>.
理斯认为贫穷导致犯罪，他还借助照片来证明自己的观点。</p><footer>2008 陕西</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>prove sth to sb:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Just give me a chance and I’ll prove it to you.
给我一个机会，我会证明给你看。</p></div>

<p>注: 表示向某人证明某事时应该用prove sth to sb，而不能用prove sb sth。<br />
- prove sb / sth (to be) + adj / n:</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They put me in prison, but, in the end, I was proved innocent.
他们把我关进监狱，但我最终被证明是清白的。</p><footer>北师大③ – 3</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He proved himself (to be) a better driver than the world champion.
他证明了自己的驾驶技术胜过世界冠军。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>prove + that / wh-从句：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Sarah wants to prove that she has brains as well as beauty.
萨拉想证明她既有美貌，又有头脑。</p><footer>译林⑦</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The challenge proved how difficult it is to drive across a desert without guidance.
这个挑战证明在没有引导的情况下开车穿越沙漠是多么的困难。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>it is proved that:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It has been proved that eating vegetables in childhood helps to protect you against serious illnesses in later life.
经证实，童年时吃蔬菜有助于日后不生大病。</p><footer>人教② – 1</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>prove oneself (to sb):</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When I first started this job, I felt I had to prove myself.
我刚开始干这份工作的时候，觉得必须证明一下自己的实力。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-turn-out">2.★ <strong>[用作系动词] 证明是；被发现是 (turn out)：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>prove+adj/n:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The book has proved very successful.
事实证明了这本书非常成功。</p><footer>人教⑧ – 3</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>prove to be sth</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He proved to be an honest friend.
事实表明他是一个诚实的朋友。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>To <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (证明) his point, Professor Brown mentioned several other experiments which had similar results.  （2013 陕西）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. prove  </p></div>